text: Dominique Damiani (12 July 1953 - 17 September 2019) was a French cyclist. She competed in the women's road race event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1953 births Category:2019 deaths Category:French female cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of France Category:Cyclists at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:People from Bourgoin-Jallieu Category:Sportspeople from Isère
